    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it doesn't feel like a \"today\" thing though. it's not just one bad day, it's like my entire soul is exhausted. there's no version of the future where this ever feels okay again. sometimes i just sit there and think about how much easier and quieter it would be if i just didn't have to wake up to this ever again. like, wouldn't that just be the ultimate rest?",
